* Configure xmonad with the testing flag:

  $ cabal configure -ftesting

* (re)Compile/install xmonad

  $ cabal build
  
  or 

  $ cabal install

* Run the tests. If installed, just run xmonad with the test argument:

  $ xmonad --run-tests

  If not installed, the run xmonad from the dist/build folder:

  ./dist/build/xmonad/xmonad --run-tests

